Le '''Slavikane chhiba''' (vai '''Slavonikane chhiba''') si [[chhib]]a le [[Slavikane sela|Slavikane selyange]], ekh familyorri andar i familiya le [[Indo-Europikane chhiba|Indo-Europikane chhibyange]]. Kadale chhiba si labyarde kai [[Estutni Europa]], bare kotora le [[Balkanurya|Balkanurenge]], kotora andar i [[Mashkarutni Europa]] thai ko nordutno  kotor la [[Asiya]]ko.

